# Project Title

Brief project description that explains purpose and core features.

## Table of Contents
- @Installation
- @Usage
- @Configuration

## Installation

```bash
npm install my-package
```

## Usage

Import and use the package:

```typescript
import { myFunction } from 'my-package';

// Example usage
const result = myFunction();
```

## Configuration

Configure the package using these options:

| Option | Type | Default | Description |
|--------|------|---------|-------------|
| `debug` | boolean | `false` | Enable debug mode |
```

